latestReleaseNotes:
### Release info
Oobee is available as a desktop app for Mac and Windows. The setup files can be downloaded under `Assets` at the bottom of the page.

### Installation Guide
* Refer to the [Installation Guide](https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/blob/master/INSTALLATION.md) for Windows and Mac.

### What's New
#### Features
* Prevent Powershell-supported features from execution when Powershell blocked in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/pull/153

#### Improvements
* Handle redirects at URL Connectivity Check, add new error codes, Skipped Documents Are Omitted in Web Crawler by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/550
* Updated URL Connectivity Error Messages, check for Oobee Backend location relative to Frontend,  speed up compile by omit squirrel distribution by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/pull/165
* Routine update playwright@1.55.0 in Oobee for stability by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/549
* Bump axios from 1.8.2 to 1.12.0 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/551
* Bump electron from 28.3.2 to 35.7.5 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/pull/159
* Bumps axios@1.12.0 electron-forge...@7.8.3 tmp@0.2.5 brace-expansion@1.1.12 debug@4.4.3 by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/pull/164
* Update playwright tests version to 1.55.0 by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/pull/166
* Update Node to LTS 22.19.0 by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/commit/0b429a9fbf3bc1b240bc5e4189807a725c96ed73

#### Bug Fixes
* Bugfix to remove logic forcing 414px for custom width on mobile by @thehansong in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/pull/161
* Resolve zip corrupt due to missing await by @WilsonkwSheng in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/548
* Local file scan throws uncaught exception if path is relative, race condition when scanning pdfs, QoL improvements by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/547
* URL Connectivity Check and Summary PDF should be headless, omit cloning Chrome/Edge profiles twice by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/553


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/compare/0.10.65...0.10.67
